{"tid":445021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尋人！12歲女童葉苑兒 失蹤6日","createTime":"2017-10-23T04:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T10:14:11.000Z","uid":48918,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":97,"replies":[{"pid":"53d4c24a788e38c32e383c20dd310b0354f88cbe","tid":445021,"uid":48918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20171023/large/1508715636_34c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171023%2Flarge%2F1508715636_34c9.jpg&h=dd96adf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12歲女童葉宛兒，上周二(17日)清晨6時半，離開藍田平田邨寓所後失蹤，其家人五日後(22日)報警。<br />\n<br />\n葉宛兒身高約1.63米，體重約38公斤，中等身材，長面型，黃皮膚，蓄長黑髮，最後露面時身穿白色校服裙及攜有一個黑色書包。<br />\n<br />\n任何人士如有葉宛兒消息或曾見過她，可致電3661 0500與觀塘警區警署人員，或與任何一間警署聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171023/57365479\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171023%2F57365479&d=%2BWG9322KYsAL9bkPqjBoJ8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=24a01d11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171023%2F57365479&h=d803de16\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171023/57365479</a>"},{"pid":"d728ad7663a12da5f8629aefe56117eef9c0ae60","tid":445021,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":25,"score":-25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:03:33.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"9b544b4b0104c61529e9cb887e762200526a52e7","tid":445021,"uid":71315,"like":39,"dislike":249,"score":-210,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:09:25.000Z","msg":"幾靚女，塊西無了"},{"pid":"323b3d8d424249aede0e8f4ce3464b3c7454db32","tid":445021,"uid":73,"like":124,"dislike":3,"score":121,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"五日後先報警?<br />\n<br />\n個女仔係咪平時成日失蹤?"},{"pid":"12790fe53ff4d2ad4aa30c462df64532f9b1ee35","tid":445021,"uid":